      <title>政策希望消退 中国股市遭遇 1 月以来最大跌幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/chinese-stocks-trim-losses-amid-signs-national-team-in-action</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国股市以今年早些时候大跌以来未曾见过的速度下跌，再次引发人们对尽管实施了政策缓冲，但市场仍将再次陷入自由落体式下跌的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/chinese-stocks-trim-losses-amid-signs-national-team-in-action</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 04:31:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
